final allowed_mutations:["add_entry_quality_filter：增加可审计的低质量入场过滤，例如避免极端 5m candle 扩张后立即追入、避免短期 ATR 异常放大时开新仓。", "add_abnormal_volatility_window_filter：仅在有限窗口内过滤异常波动，不得演变为长期 no-trade。", "pair_specific_risk_budget：对 OP/USDT、DOGE/USDT、SOL/USDT 降低高风险 setup 权重，对 BTC/USDT、BNB/USDT 保持交易数底盘。", "tighten_stoploss_contextually：允许基于波动结构微调止损触发条件，但不得用 trailing stop 替代固定 stoploss。", "improve_entry_confirmation：增加趋势确认、成交量确认、回撤确认或多指标一致性，以降低假突破止损。", "reduce_overstrict_regime_filter：若上一轮 too_few_trades，允许降低过严 regime filter。", "controlled_widen_entry：若交易数低于 20 或接近 20，允许受控放宽入场阈值，但仅针对非坏 pair 或低风险 setup。", "pair_specific_restore_non_bad_pairs：若全局过滤误杀 BTC/USDT、BNB/USDT 的有效交易，允许恢复这些 pair 的部分入场。", "relax_global_filter：若 min_trades 不达标，允许放松全局过滤器，但需保留高 beta pair 的局部风险控制。", "controlled_widen_entry", "relax_global_filter", "pair_specific_restore_non_bad_pairs", "reduce_overstrict_regime_filter", "slightly_lower_breakout_confirmation_threshold", "slightly_reduce_trend_strength_threshold_for_BTC_SOL_BNB", "enable_earlier_breakeven_transition_after_partial_profit", "add_staged_profit_taking_before_full_roi_target", "tighten_time_based_exit_for_stalled_trades", "pair_specific_position_sizing_with_lower_size_on_high_beta_pairs", "retain_abnormal_volatility_window_filter_but_shorten_its_blocking_duration", "prefer_pullback_continuation_entries_over_late_candle_chase", "controlled_widen_entry: 放宽 entry 触发条件（如扩大 EMA 偏差容忍度、降低成交量门槛），修复 stoploss_to_roi_high 过早止损问题", "relax_global_filter: 适度放宽全局 regime 过滤器（如降低 ADX/波动率最低门槛），防止 too_few_trades", "pair_specific_restore_non_bad_pairs: 对非历史 bad_pair 的 OP/USDT 和 DOGE/USDT 恢复小仓位 entry 权限", "reduce_overstrict_regime_filter: 如当前 regime filter 导致 trades < 20，必须放宽至允许 risk_off 中性状态下的突破 entry", "widen_stoploss_threshold: 针对 stoploss_to_roi_high failure，适当扩大止损空间（如从 -2% 扩至 -3% 至 -3.5%），减少过早止损", "add_volume_confirmation_for_breakout: 用成交量扩张作为突破确认，提高动量 entry 精度，减少假突破亏损", "controlled_widen_entry: 在 DXY 回落窗口或流动性改善信号下，适度放宽入场条件以恢复交易数", "relax_global_filter: 当前全局 regime_filter 疑似过紧（导致 too_few_trades），允许对非 bad_pair 放宽一档阈值", "pair_specific_restore_non_bad_pairs: 对未被标记为持续亏损对的品种，恢复其正常入场权限", "reduce_overstrict_regime_filter: 如 regime_filter 导致连续多根 K 线全部过滤，允许降低过滤灵敏度一档", "stoploss_tighten_absolute: 针对 stoploss_to_roi_high 失败类型，允许收窄 stoploss 绝对值（如从 -4% 收至 -2.5%）", "roi_table_multi_tier: 允许将单一 ROI 目标拆分为多档位（时间-收益率阶梯），以降低持仓时间过长的 tail_risk", "controlled_widen_entry: loosen entry score threshold by ≤10% to recover trade count if too_few_trades", "relax_global_filter: reduce global regime strictness if current filter produces <20 trades in backtest", "pair_specific_restore_non_bad_pairs: re-enable OP/USDT and DOGE/USDT if blocked without confirmed bad_pair evidence", "reduce_overstrict_regime_filter: if risk_off filter is blocking >50% of valid signals, convert to soft penalty (position-size reduction) rather than hard block", "roi_ladder_adjustment: adjust ROI steps to account for stoploss_to_roi_high failure pattern — lower intermediate ROI targets", "volatility_normalized_position_sizing: scale position size by pair-specific ATR regime", "pair_specific_limit_bad_pairs", "tighten_loss_tail_via_pair_specific_rules"]
